or também foi apreendido em madeireira (Foto: Polícia Ambiental de Jaci-Paraná/4PEL-PA)\" width=\"524\" height=\"686\" data-src=\"https://s2.glbimg.com/skdNYthZM0akak8Xqbl8JgMP_aI=/0x45:585x811/984x0/smart/filters:strip_icc()/i.s3.glbimg.com/v1/AUTH_59edd422c0c84a879bd37670ae4f538a/internal_photos/bs/2018/s/G/ElKRUHSg6jp8uvU48aAQ/8c16e002-9334-4f7a-9b22-183ac284ebc8.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-track-category=\"Link no Texto\" data-track-links=\"\">Trator também foi apreendido em madeireira (Foto: Polícia Ambiental de Jaci-Paraná/4PEL-PA)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>','Caminhão com 9 toras de madeira é apreendido em madeireira de RO','Flagrante ocorreu no distrito de Jaci-Paraná pela Polícia Ambiental. Suspeitos foram autuados por crimes ambientais, segundo polícia.','inherit','closed','closed','','4817-revision-v1','','','2018-05-15 16:03:44','2018-05-15 19:03:44','',4817,'http://localhost/folha-do-comercio/?p=4819',0,'revision','',0),(4820,1,'2018-05-15 16:04:56','2018-05-15 19:04:56','','bg-1','','inherit','closed','closed','','bg-1','','','2018-05-15 16:04:56','2018-05-15 19:04:56','',2811,'http://localhost/folha-do-comercio/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/bg-1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(4821,1,'2018-05-15 16:29:41','2018-05-15 19:29:41','[bt_section layout=\"boxed\" top_spaced=\"topMediumSpaced\" bottom_spaced=\"bottomMediumSpaced\" skin=\"light\" full_screen=\"no\" vertical_align=\"inherit\" divider=\"no\" back_image=\"\" back_color=\"#ffffff\" back_overlay=\"\" back_video=\"\" video_settings=\"\" back_video_mp4=\"\" back_video_ogg=\"\" back_video_webm=\"\" parallax=\"\" parallax_offset=\"\" animation=\"\" animation_back=\"\" animation_impress=\"\" posts_category=\"\" posts_author=\"\" show_prev=\"\" show_sticky=\"\" el_id=\"\" el_class=\"\" el_style=\"\"][bt_row][bt_column width=\"1/3\" align=\"left\" vertical_align=\"inherit\" border=\"no_border\" cell_padding=\"default\" animation=\"no_animation\" highlight=\"no_highlight\" background_col